item.title: 2021 Xplore Code Camp W 1
item.description: Day 1: Graphics Primitives # We learned how to use point(), line(), stroke(), strokeWeight(), background(), and fill() to make graphical objects appear in a p5js sketch. Random Follow the Mouse, by M.J.
